'''图鲁纳德'''(图鲁语: ತುಳುನಾಡು),指[[印度|印度]][[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]、[[卡纳塔克邦|卡纳塔克邦]]使用[[图鲁语|图鲁语]]的地区。该地区滨临[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]。图鲁纳德总面积8,441 km<sup>2</sup>(3,259 sq mi)，总人口3,005,897（2001）。

== 分离主义诉求 ==
图鲁纳德的[[图鲁人|图鲁人]]要求将[[图鲁语|图鲁语]]列为[[官方语言|官方语言]]，并单独成立一个民族邦。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.daijiworld.com/news/news_disp.asp?n_id=27089&n_tit=News+headlines |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-05-24 |archive-date=2010-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101124044553/http://www.daijiworld.com/news/news_disp.asp?n_id=27089&n_tit=News+headlines |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/03/06/stories/2008030658140300.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-05-24 |archive-date=2011-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110821030433/http://www.hindu.com/2008/03/06/stories/2008030658140300.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

